### Edit a Movement [PUT]

Edit a field for a movement.

+ description (string, optional) - The description of the movement.
+ price (string, optional) - The amount of the transaction.
+ type (string, optional) - The type of the movement.
+ created_at (string, optional) - The date of the transaction.

+ Request (application/json)

        {
            "movement": {
                            "price": "1000"
                        }
        }

+ Response 204

